---
import Eyebrow from "./ui/Eyebrow.astro";
import Node from "./ui/Node.astro";
---

<section id="principle">
  <div class="wrap">
    <Eyebrow>The method</Eyebrow>
    <h2>Design is a chain of tradeoffs,<br />not a stack of best practices.</h2>
    <p class="lead">Every answer follows the same three moves — the same shape as the mark.</p>
    <div class="triad">
      <Node hue="b" n="01" title="State the constraint">
        Traffic pattern, consistency need, latency budget, team reality. No numbers? Assume out loud.
      </Node>
      <Node hue="t" n="02" title="Pick the option">
        Reuse before build, managed before self-hosted, boring before novel. Name the one that fits.
      </Node>
      <Node hue="a" n="03" title="Name the tradeoff">
        Every choice costs something — consistency, ops burden, latency, money. Say it plainly.
      </Node>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
